{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_011vo7xs1gfw55mCpxcRBCqZ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01D939MGvdPbJCm9gATWY9xQ","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Cranberry Orange Tart.generated.22.txt","content":"CRANBERRY ORANGE TART\n\nThis beautiful tart brings together the bright, zesty\nflavor of citrus with the tartness of winter cranberries.\nI first tasted this at a small bistro in Lyon, where the pastry\nchef prepared it with a special touch. The combination of\nthe buttery crust, smooth custard filling, and jewel-like\ncranberries creates something truly memorable. It's perfect\nfor holiday gatherings or an elegant dinner party.\n\nINGREDIENTS:\n\nPastry Crust:\n- 250g all-purpose flour\n- 125g cold butter, cubed\n- 1 egg yolk\n- 2 tablespoons ice water\n- 1/2 teaspoon salt\n- 1 tablespoon sugar\n\nFilling:\n- 200g fresh cranberries (frozen also works)\n- Zest and juice of 2 oranges\n- 100g sugar\n- 75g custard powder\n- 300ml whole milk\n- 2 egg yolks\n- 1 tablespoon butter\n\nGlaze:\n- 100g orange marmalade, warmed\n- 1 tablespoon water\n\nINSTRUCTIONS:\n\nMake pastry: blend flour, salt, sugar. Cut in cold butter.\nAdd egg yolk and ice water, mix until dough forms.\nChill 30 minutes.\nRoll out and line 9-inch tart pan.\nPrick bottom and chill 15 minutes.\nBake blind at 200°C for 12 minutes.\nMake custard: whisk egg yolks with sugar.\nHeat milk and pour over yolks, stirring constantly.\nReturn to heat, add custard powder, cook until thick.\nAdd orange zest and juice.\nCool slightly, fold in butter.\nPour into crust. Arrange cranberries on top.\nBake at 180°C for 20 minutes until set.\nGlaze with warm marmalade.\nCool completely before serving.\nServes 8."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":768,"cache_read_input_tokens":115974,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":768},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"71a8c6f6-257f-4eaf-b936-2ff6b59e51c0","uuid":"0dc4eda2-7bac-4cd2-a0b1-d041e3815e7f"}
